Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\N this world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly \Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:44.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:44.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:48.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:48.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:53.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:53.28,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:04.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:04.71,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:09.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:09.25,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:14.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:14.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:16.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:16.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner (･∀･)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner :D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:25.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:25.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:30.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:30.94,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:33.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:33.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:37.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:37.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:41.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:41.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
